          <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Protect the Gig Economy Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill amends Rule 23 of the Federal Rules of Civil Procedure to expand the preliminary requirements for class certification in a class action lawsuit to include a new requirement that the claim does not allege misclassification of employees as independent contractors.</p>]]></text>
